| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-3631 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhub)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 1b9b2fca-9c50-5262-aa6c-2ed367d0e6ed"
